WEBVTT

00:03:28.520 --> 00:03:33.256
And that was because the computer
could make decisions much faster,

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.536
it could process a lot more information

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:38.960
and it can process decisions much more --

00:03:39.880 --> 00:03:41.080
less emotionally.

00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:46.680
So it radically improved
my decision-making.

00:03:48.440 --> 00:03:53.336
Eight years after I started Bridgewater,

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:54.896
I had my greatest failure,

00:03:54.920 --> 00:03:56.120
my greatest mistake.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:59.816
It was late 1970s,

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:01.816
I was 34 years old,